{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_38","type":"command_execution","command":"/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,80p' NOTES.md\"","aggregated_output":"Fixed:\n- Completion now filters by the typed prefix and includes `fn name(...)` function signatures.\n- Parser recovery reports missing closing braces and still builds later symbols/diagnostics.\n- Go-to-definition prefers local bindings, including parameters, over same-named functions.\n- Comment text is ignored for diagnostics and completion prefix detection.\n- `didChange` reparses full-text updates, replaces stale diagnostics, and remains idempotent.\n\nStill open:\n- None from the current defect list.\n\nVerifier pass 2026-06-07:\n- Re-ran `npm test`; all current LSP behavior tests pass.\n- Checked UTF-8 framed transport and range-based `didChange`; no `src/` changes were needed.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
